    "summary": "I am a Senior Consultant with a proven experience in Information Technology. I managed multiple IT-related projects leading teams and supporting > 10 client companies in the Energy & Utilities, Automotive, Insurance, Aerospace business across Italy, France, Spain, LATAM and the Netherlands. \n\nI have extensive knowledge of IT governance (COBIT 2019, ITIL v4, ISO 27001), project management (CAPM), agile management (PSMI, Atlassian Confluence & JIRA), digital transformation and IT consulting. Having developed people management and leadership skills, I have proven track of succeeding in leading teams and managing projects aimed at enhancing technology solutions and defining the IT strategy in complex organizations. I am proficient in public speaking, having held all-hands training sessions about digital transformation, IT compliance and software adoption in multiple organizations.\nI gained a Master of Science in International Business and Management at the Newcastle University Business School and University of Groningen: I am fluent in several languages (native Italian, proficient English, and intermediate French) and I am familiar with working worldwide with people from different cultures.\n\nHere are some insights into my latest accomplishments: \n\u2022 I collaborated with the CEO and the Top Management Team supporting the Change Management activities aimed at the 21.000 employees of a newly acquired company (focus: IT, HR, Accounting)\n\u2022 I led a team in the definition of an IT strategy and the design of an IT process compliant to the company procedures, leading the Change Management activities aimed at > 500 people in the IT and BSN departments\n\u2022 I led > 30 training sessions aimed at > 500 people in the IT and BSN departments with success rate feedback of 9.4 /10 gained from the participants, being identified as a Subject Matter Expery within the company\n\u2022 I managed the development of a mobile App aimed at B2C and B2B customers, leading the Development and the Testing team across US, Italy and Poland: the company registered a 75% customer base increase over the first three months from App release into market\n\nI am excited about the latest trends in IT (Web3, Metaverse, AI, IoT). I am also very interested in topics like leadership, entrepreneurship, critical thinking, people management and creativity applied to management.",
